00:15:43.510 --> 00:15:46.850
and classes and now
her own foundation.

00:15:46.850 --> 00:15:50.080
She has been invited twice
by First Lady Michelle Obama

00:15:50.080 --> 00:15:52.320
to the White House
for her outreach

00:15:52.320 --> 00:15:56.080
to help families live
happier and healthier lives.

00:15:56.080 --> 00:16:01.350
And she received the 2014
Southern Foodways Alliance John

00:16:01.350 --> 00:16:05.090
