00:17:17.680 --> 00:17:19.080
and many other things.

00:17:19.080 --> 00:17:24.370
I'm not going to talk
about her collection,

00:17:24.370 --> 00:17:26.260
she's going to talk a
little bit about it I think

00:17:26.260 --> 00:17:28.180
in relation with the book.

00:17:28.180 --> 00:17:32.010
But the Jemima Code is
also the title of her blog

00:17:32.010 --> 00:17:35.650
and a traveling exhibit which
